Class BOXParcel

  • java.lang.Object
    • Parcel
      • BOXParcel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    computesFee

    public class BOXParcel
extends Parcel
    The class BOXParcel is an extension of the Parcel class, that inherits the attributes of the Parcel class. The BOXParcel class also represents a Box Parcel object that has a boolean attribute as to whether the Box Parcel contains an irregular object or not. the Box Parcel also has a regular rate, volumetric weight rate, and actual weight rate.
